flowchart TD
    A[Start: alma_multiply] --> B[Validate inputs]
    B --> C{n <= 256?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Single BLAS dgemm]
    C -->|No| E[Block partition matrix]
    E --> F{For each block pair}
    F --> G[Classify block: SVD]
    G --> H{Dense or LowRank?}
    H -->|Dense| I[BLAS dgemm]
    H -->|LowRank| J[U*S*VT multiply]
    I --> K[Accumulate result]
    J --> K
    F -->|done| L[End]
    D --> L
    
    style A fill:#f9f,stroke:#333
    style G fill:#ff9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style I fill:#90EE90,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style J fill:#90EE90,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style L fill:#90EE90,stroke:#333
